<hr>
<h2>游勞板</h2>
<p>30歲，謝堡企業老闆，與建仁企業為競爭關係，受邀擔任測試員</p>
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/k6nlJ9k.jpg" style="width: 100%"/>
</body>
<script>
    async function logout() {
        await $.ajax({
            url: '/logout',
            type: 'POST',
            cache: false,
            data: false,
            success: function (data) {
                console.log('Success!')
            },
            error: function (jqXHR, textStatus, err) {
                console.log('text status ' + textStatus + ', err ' + err)
            }
        })
        location.reload();
    }

    function start() {
        location.href = '/';
    }
    function map() {
        location.href = '/map';
    }
</script>
</html>